{"word":"G2318 - θεοσεβής - theosebḗs - theh-os-eb-ace' - Worshipper of God","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεοσεβής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">theosebḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">theh-os-eb-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Worshipper of God</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவபக்தியுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"worshipping God, pious"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2316 - θεός - theós - theh'-os/2316\">G2316</a> and <a href=\"#/G4576 - σέβομαι - sébomai - seb'-om-ahee/4576\">G4576</a>; <i>reverent of God</i>, that is, <i>pious:</i> - worshipper of God.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2317/2317\">G2317</a>, <a href=\"#/G2318/2318\">G2318</a>"}]}